snippet.title: 🦘Dinkum Together Official Trailer
snippet.description:
G’Day, pioneers! Explore a mysterious island as you build a town all your own. Boundless adventures await you in Dinkum Together!
'Dinkum Together' is a pioneer life simulation game currently being developed by 5minlab, a Krafton studio, for multiple platforms. It’s based on 'Dinkum,' the beloved survival life sim created by Australian developer James Bendon.

Stay in the loop by following our official channels for all the latest updates and exciting surprises! 
🦘 Dinkum Together Official Channels 
👉 Website: https://dinkum.news/WEB
👉 YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@DinkumTogether

※ This video contains footage captured during the development stage.

 #Dinkumtogether #Dinkum #Krafton #OfficialTrailer
